  "text": "3.2.1. Recession operator and ergodicity conditions. To characterize the ergodicity of a perfect-information stochastic game with finite state space, we shall use, along the lines of [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] , the recession operator associated with the Shapley operator T : R n → R n . This operator is a self-map of R n defined by",
